"Today's cyber criminals are smarter than ever and it's likely that we are yet to see the most advanced attacks. With an estimated global cost of around $6tr (£4.24tr) per year attributed to cybercrime, there can be no denying that digital crime is just as lucrative for criminals as it is destructive to businesses. 1 Today's cyber criminals are smarter than ever and it's likely that we are yet to see the most advanced attacks. Ransomware, in particular, has proven to be a devastating and constantly morphing form of attack. Yet there is a lot that companies can do to prepare. Taking steps to outsmart the new technologies that criminals are employing is key. Florian Malecki of StorageCraft outlines the steps you can take to protect your organisation."
